PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775848268
OL,3,CMen jailed for setting 82-year-old
OL,4,Cgran's home alight while she slept
OL,6,FFour men have been jailed for setting
OL,7,Ffire to an 82-year-old woman's house
OL,8,Fas part of a criminal vendetta.
OL,10,FThe men, aged from 19 to 33 and all
OL,11,Ffrom the Weston-super-Mare area,
OL,12,Flaunched the arson attack on a house
OL,13,Fin Ferndale, Rhondda Cynon Taf, in
OL,14,FJuly last year.
OL,16,FCCTV footage showed two of them
OL,17,Fapproaching the front of the house
OL,18,Fholding petrol jerry cans, whilst
OL,19,Fanother of the men filmed on his phone.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775848268
OL,3,CMen jailed for setting 82-year-old
OL,4,Cgran's home alight while she slept
OL,6,FLuckily the woman, who had been asleep
OL,7,Fdownstairs in the property, was
OL,8,Falerted to the noise of smashing glass
OL,9,Fand was able to get out safely with
OL,10,Fhelp from neighbours and officers.
OL,12,FSouth Wales Police' Senior
OL,13,FInvestigating Officer, Detective
OL,14,FInspector Owain Morrison said it was
OL,15,F"only by luck" that the attack had not
OL,16,Fbeen fatal.
OL,18,FAuryn Gustur, 19, Connor Pitt, 24,
OL,19,FAlfie Wheeler, 19, and Lewis Manito,
OL,20,F33, attacked the home on Protheroe
OL,21,FStreet in the early hours of 28 July.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775848268
OL,3,CMen jailed for setting 82-year-old
OL,4,Cgran's home alight while she slept
OL,6,FWheeler and Gustur had been driven to
OL,7,Fthe area by 19-year-old Storm Truman,
OL,8,Fwhere they then met with Pitt - who
OL,9,Fhad been driven to south Wales by
OL,10,FLewis Manito.
OL,12,FWheeler, Gustur and Pitt, armed with
OL,13,Ftwo jerry cans of petrol, were driven
OL,14,Fto Protheroe Street by Truman, where
OL,15,Fthey carried out the attack.
OL,17,FPolice were alerted to the fire at
OL,18,Faround 1:25am and by 1:50am, the four
OL,19,Fwere in custody
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775848268
OL,3,CMen jailed for setting 82-year-old
OL,4,Cgran's home alight while she slept
OL,6,FAn accelerant was used to ignite the
OL,7,Ffire, which immediately engulfed the
OL,8,Ffront of the house and the cars
OL,9,Foutside the address. The elderly
OL,10,Fvictim was asleep downstairs but was
OL,11,Fwoken by the sound of glass smashing.
OL,13,FShe could be heard screaming on CCTV
OL,14,Fas the house ignited.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775848268
OL,3,CMen jailed for setting 82-year-old
OL,4,Cgran's home alight while she slept
OL,6,FWith help from neighbours and
OL,7,Fofficers, the victim managed to escape
OL,8,Fthe house safely, whilst the four fled
OL,9,Ffrom the scene. Emergency services
OL,10,Farrived on the street moments later
OL,11,Fand a major incident was later
OL,12,Fdeclared.
OL,14,FApproximately #650,000 worth of damage
OL,15,Fwas caused to three properties, their
OL,16,Fcontents and a car.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775848268
OL,3,CMen jailed for setting 82-year-old
OL,4,Cgran's home alight while she slept
OL,6,FEyewitnesses reported seeing a
OL,7,Fsuspicious car in the street
OL,8,Fimmediately before the fire and were
OL,9,Fable to give a partial registration
OL,10,Fnumber to police.
OL,12,FThe car was then identified driving
OL,13,Falong the A470 and a stinger device
OL,14,Fwas used to puncture the tyres and to
OL,15,Fstop the vehicle.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775848268
OL,3,CMen jailed for setting 82-year-old
OL,4,Cgran's home alight while she slept
OL,6,FThose inside the car were arrested and
OL,7,Fofficers found a machete, hammer,
OL,8,Fgloves and a balaclava inside the
OL,9,Fvehicle. The sat nav also showed that
OL,10,Fthe address in Protheroe Street had
OL,11,Fbeen entered into it as a destination.
OL,13,FAnalysis of mobile phones seized from
OL,14,Fthe car then identified Lewis Manito's
OL,15,Finvolvement in the attack and he was
OL,16,Farrested by Avon and Somerset Police
OL,17,Fin August 2025.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775848268
OL,3,CMen jailed for setting 82-year-old
OL,4,Cgran's home alight while she slept
OL,6,FGustur pleaded guilty to arson with
OL,7,Fintent to endanger life and was
OL,8,Fsentenced to 15-and-a-half years in
OL,9,Fprison.
OL,11,FPitt pleaded guilty to arson with
OL,12,Fintent to endanger life and was
OL,13,Fsentenced to 18 years in prison.
OL,15,FWheeler pleaded guilty to arson with
OL,16,Fintent to endanger life and possession
OL,17,Fof a bladed article and was sentenced
OL,18,Fto 13 years in prison.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775848268
OL,3,CMen jailed for setting 82-year-old
OL,4,Cgran's home alight while she slept
OL,6,FManito pleaded guilty to arson
OL,7,Frecklessly endangering life and
OL,8,Fperverting the course of justice and
OL,9,Fwas sentenced to nine years in prison.
OL,11,FStorm Truman was found not guilty of
OL,12,Farson.
OL,14,FDetective Inspector Owain Morrison
OL,15,Fsaid: "This was a cowardly attack on
OL,16,Fthe home of an 82-year-old woman,
OL,17,Forganised and directed by a criminal
OL,18,Ffigure due to a debt linked to the
OL,19,Fvictim's family member. The victim was
OL,20,Fwholly innocent.
OL,26,@wD@GOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775848268
OL,3,CMen jailed for setting 82-year-old
OL,4,Cgran's home alight while she slept
OL,6,F"Those that carried out the attack did
OL,7,Fso for financial gain. They had little
OL,8,Fcare of the consequences for the
OL,9,Fperson in the house or their
OL,10,Fneighbours. They would have heard the
OL,11,Fvictim screaming as they ignited the
OL,12,Ffire and made off from the scene. It
OL,13,Fis only by luck this was not a fatal
OL,14,Fattack.
OL,16,F"The professionalism of our Roads
OL,17,FPolicing Unit meant that four men were
OL,18,Fpromptly arrested as they made their
OL,19,Fway to the M4.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775848268
OL,3,CMen jailed for setting 82-year-old
OL,4,Cgran's home alight while she slept
OL,6,F"A team of dedicated investigators
OL,7,Fworked tirelessly to gather key
OL,8,Fevidence and identify other persons
OL,9,Fdirectly involved in the attack and
OL,10,Fbring them to justice.
OL,12,F"I would like to thank DC Cath Moore,
OL,13,Fthe Officer in the Case, for her care
OL,14,Fand attention in building a compelling
OL,15,Fbody of evidence for the Crown
OL,16,FProsecution Service to present to the
OL,17,Fcourt which is reflected in the guilty
OL,18,Fpleas.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775848268
OL,3,CMen jailed for setting 82-year-old
OL,4,Cgran's home alight while she slept
OL,6,F"Above all I would like to thank the
OL,7,Fvictim in this case, and their family,
OL,8,Ffor their courage and patience whilst
OL,9,Fwe investigated this matter.
OL,11,F"I would like to re-assure the
OL,12,Fcommunity that the investigation to
OL,13,Fidentify the person who directed this
OL,14,Fattack and bring them to justice is
OL,15,Fongoing."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@IO]
